{"tid":1426637,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全新 民間記者會產生辦法","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T06:44:11.000Z","uid":151057,"like":25,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"895649dd1b2e3063f5dfb64b719c7c23babed534","tid":1426637,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:14:41.000Z","msg":"用意：<br />\n1） 解決代表性不足之問題<br />\n2） 解決無法回答記者提問之困局<br />\n3） 解決原組織無足夠資源每日開展記者會之難處<br />\n<br />\n機制：<br />\nA）澄清民間記者會不是代表市民大眾，<br />\n而是示威人士與公眾對話的橋樑。<br />\nB）每日記者會分兩部份：「朗讀對公眾訊息發佈時間」及「記者發問時間」。<br />\nC）記者發問間時，問題將不會即場解答，而是經連登相討後，第二日在「朗讀對公眾訊息發佈時間」。<br />\nD）「朗讀對公眾訊息發佈時間」除回答記者問題還會加上每日對警方及政府新指控。<br />\nE）發言人士衹是照稿讀，收集問題，不須有任何個人立場之發問，亦不用負責任何責任，甚至可以由非示威者代表宣言。<br />\nF）每日中午結束後會在連登及TG由連登仔開始文稿工作。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各位支持"},{"pid":"ad39f1aa0ec103832f4ac995801f704db01cff3f","tid":1426637,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:15:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51ab5f5926a68fefcbb933424b6e4859bba55f71","tid":1426637,"uid":276162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecdf164246a021cbea447486a12bfd5cbe995e2","tid":1426637,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:16:40.000Z","msg":"如果唔係記者會可能一直停播"},{"pid":"6371633fb9c7c42ac90032f7953e59a02f2e4565","tid":1426637,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:20:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676c9a8a537f15c6f253dc7c5903df0396752f3c","tid":1426637,"uid":268656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:20:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae1c7391f10a351b22d2e14b82da9010f7b8e6d5","tid":1426637,"uid":151057,"like":0,"dislike":